        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "Some Grave Talk In Gay Company",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000002_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000002_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "He shook hands with her warmly, and looked inquiringly in her face, and then drew her into a quiet corner in a window seat, where they could talk without being much observed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000002_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000002_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "Elsie did not sit beside them, but left them to their own conversation, assured that she would hear all that she cared to know by and by; yet she was not neglected, for Miss Rennie had taken a great fancy to her, and was determined, if possible, to get her partners.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000002_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000002_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "Miss Rennie had judged hardly of Jane's personal appearance at first sight, but she thought Elsie a most elegant and interesting creature.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "\"No news,\" said Jane.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "\"I wrote to you of Elsie's last bitter disappointment.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "\"Ah!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "Jane, my cup of prosperity has very many bitter drops in it.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "If any one had told me beforehand of these months that I have passed since my uncle's death, I should have thought them absolutely intolerable, and would have preferred death. But there is no human lot without its mitigations and ameliorations. God tempers the wind to the shorn lamb.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "I am not happy, perhaps; but I am not miserable.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000009_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000009_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "He will make a figure in the world, and I will help him to do so.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "\"Very much, indeed; all the more as I acquired the language.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "\"So far as I can see, she appears to be happy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "\"Indeed!\" said Jane, \"I thought it would have pleased you to be acknowledged.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "I had a mother who did not care for me, and a father who did his duty, as he fancied, by me, but who disliked me, and they appear to have hated one another.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000024_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000024_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "She was prettier than her daughter, at least in repose; but neither of them were at all like my ideal; for I forgot the French class of face, and embodied my fancy portraits in an English type.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "\"Very much, indeed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "The art of conversing these French people carry to great perfection.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000028_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000028_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "I should like to try an experiment.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000028_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000028_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "You know that sand flat, that is worth very little but for scanty pasture, at the back of the Black Hill, as it is called.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "\"What an excellent idea!\" said Jane.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000030_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000030_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "I have got plans for the cottages which I wanted you to look at this morning; I think they will do.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "\"You must let Peggy see them; she was brought up in one of those cottages you speak of, and will know all their deficiencies.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "It will set a good example to the neighbourhood,\" said Jane.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "\"And, after all, it will not cost me more to build these cottages, and make thirty families more comfortable and more self respecting, than it would to enlarge Cross Hall, as mr Chalmers advises me strongly to do-by building a new wing and adding a conservatory in the place of your modest little greenhouse.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000032_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000032_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "Our picked men, and many of our picked women, emigrate to America and Australia.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000032_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000032_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "I confess that if I were in their place I should do the same; but let my experiment succeed, it may be imitated.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "I will watch the result with the greatest interest.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000033_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000033_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "You know nothing could give me greater pleasure than your success in such a noble work,\" said Jane, with sparkling eyes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000037_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000037_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "For myself, I think just as highly of my own abilities and acquirements as ever I did.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000037_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000037_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "I am sorry that your minister has left his church, for I hoped to become acquainted with him; and he looked so cheerful that I thought he might do Elsie good. This new clergyman does not strike me as being so genial or kindly, though I certainly like his sermons and his devotional services very much.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "\"Can you not place your sister in the same care?\" asked Francis.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "\"How did our friends get acquainted with mr Dalzell?\" said Jane.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000043_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000043_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "mr Dalzell, I forgot you.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000045_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000045_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "Miss Wilson was ward of mrs Rennie's, as Jane had heard, a West Indian heiress, somewhat stupid, and very much impressed with her own wealth and importance.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000045_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000045_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "She had just left school, having made all the progress which money without natural ability or any of the usual incentives to application could attain, and was to live at the Rennies', which she thought a very dull place.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2920_156224_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2920/156224/2920_156224_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2920",
        "content": "\"Now,\" said Miss Rennie, \"I have done my best for mr Dalzell.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
